'''''Cetobacterium''''' is a [[Gram-negative]], [[Pleomorphism (microbiology)|pleomorphic]], non-[[spore]]-forming, [[rod-shaped]] and non-motile  genus of bacteria from the family of [[Fusobacteriaceae]].<ref name=Cetobacterium/><ref>{{cite journal |title=Cetobacterium |website=www.uniprot.org |url=https://www.uniprot.org/taxonomy/180162 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Parker |first1=Charles Thomas |last2=Osier |first2=Nicole Danielle |last3=Garrity |first3=George M |title=Taxonomic Abstract for the genera |journal=The NamesforLife Abstracts |date=1 January 2003 |doi=10.1601/tx.8394 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last1=Edwards |first1=Kirstin J. |last2=Logan |first2=Julie M. J. |last3=Gharbia |first3=Saheer E. |title=Cetobacterium |journal=Bergey's Manual of Systematics of Archaea and Bacteria |date=14 September 2015 |pages=1–3 |doi=10.1002/9781118960608.gbm00767 |language=en|isbn=9781118960608 }}</ref>

