io Institute for Studies in Education (OISE) |Canada conference |1977-05-00 |1977-05-00 |- |1977 |{{flagu|United States}} |Cocoa Beach |United States |n/a |1st Joint Canada/U.S. IASSIST conference |1977-02-16 |1977-02-20 |}
==History== The first IASSIST conference was held in 1977 in Cocoa Beach, Florida <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chass.utoronto.ca/datalib/iassist/iass77.htm |title=IASSIST 1977 Conference Archive |publisher=IASSIST |access-date=2016-05-30 |deadurl=unfit |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060517162320/http://www.chass.utoronto.ca/datalib/iassist/iass77.htm |archivedate=May 17, 2006 }}</ref> with 29 representatives from Canada and the United States.
